dataIdInfo.idPurp: This shapefile represents the current management area for the Hawaii pelagic stock of false killer whales.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This shapefile represents the current management area for the Hawaii pelagic stock of false killer whales. This boundary is based on biological data as described in Oleson et al. 2023. More information on false killer whale stocks around the Hawaiian Islands can be found in the latest stock assessment report.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: This shapefile was created by Amanda Bradford <amanda.bradford@noaa.gov> at the NOAA Fisheries Pacific Islands Fisheries Science Center. The current projection is WGS_1984_UTM_Zone_4N.
